text: Daedalichthys is an extinct genus of palaeoniscoid fish from the Lower Triassic period. Not much is known about it, but experts may suggest it is 20 cm long. == Related pages == * List of prehistoric bony fish genera * Palaeoperca * Serranidae == References == # Sepkoski, Jack (2002).
